Property Decorator:
    - It is a inbuilt decorator which help us to define the method in such a way that we can use it as a property without parenthesis.
    - Syntax:
        class className:
            @property
            def methodName(self):
                #Method Body
    - We can also define setter and deleter for the property method.
    -Syntax:
        class className:
            @property
            def methodName(self):
                #Method body

            @methodName.setter
            def methodName(self, value):
                #Method body

            @methodNme.deleter
            def methodName(self):
                #Method body

